size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>FORMATO FINAL PARA PUBLICA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Manuscrito final para publica&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; aquele com as corre&ccedil;&otilde;es feitas e aceitas pelos&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>consultores e editores. Dever&aacute; ser mantida a mesma formata&ccedil;&atilde;o da vers&atilde;o submetida.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Os "tipos e tamanhos de arquivos" ser&atilde;o os aqueles &nbsp;indicados nos procedimentos de&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>submiss&atilde;o (ver itens (a) e (b) em "1. PREPARA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O PARA SUBMISS&Atilde;O" no in&iacute;cio&nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>desta se&ccedil;&atilde;o. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>IV - Itens de Verifica&ccedil;&atilde;o para Submiss&atilde;o &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Como parte do processo de submiss&atilde;o, os autores s&atilde;o obrigados a verificar a&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>conformidade da submiss&atilde;o em rela&ccedil;&atilde;o a todos os itens listados a seguir. As submiss&otilde;es&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>que n&atilde;o estiverem de acordo com as normas ser&atilde;o devolvidas aos autores. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>A contribui&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; original e in&eacute;dita, e n&atilde;o foi submetida para publica&ccedil;&atilde;o em outra&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>revista; caso contr&aacute;rio, justificar em "Coment&aacute;rios ao Editor". &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>O arquivo para submiss&atilde;o est&aacute; em formato Microsoft &nbsp;Word, bem como uma c&oacute;pia em pdf, com texto em espa&ccedil;o&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>simples e fonte de 11 pontos, em Times New Roman. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>O manuscrito, quando submetido, dever&aacute; ser enviado &nbsp;em arquivo contendo apenas o&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>texto (formato doc), e cada ilustra&ccedil;&atilde;o e tabela dever&aacute; vir em arquivo separado (formato&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>tif para as figuras). Id&ecirc;ntico procedimento ser&aacute; adotado no envio do manuscrito final&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>para publica&ccedil;&atilde;o, ap&oacute;s as &uacute;ltimas corre&ccedil;&otilde;es. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Nenhum arquivo poder&aacute; ultrapassar a 10Mb, tanto de texto como de ilustra&ccedil;&atilde;o. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>O artigo n&atilde;o foi particionado, permitindo o entendimento integral e independente do seu&nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>conte&uacute;do. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>O artigo n&atilde;o excede a 10.000 palavras e 20 p&aacute;ginas em documento word.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 25, 'active', '2015-05-14 14:58:59', '2015-05-14 15:30:02', NULL),
	(37, 35, 'rbgea-diretrizes', 'Diretrizes para Autores', '<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><strong><big>PREPARA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O PARA SUBMISS&Atilde;O</big></strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Tipo e Tamanho de Arquivo: O texto do manuscrito dever&aacute; ser enviado&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>em arquivo &nbsp;Word (.doc), &nbsp;em separado, com os locais de inser&ccedil;&atilde;o das&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>figuras assinalados, seguido das respectivas legendas. As ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es</big></span></span></span> <span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>dever&atilde;o ser enviadas em arquivo .tif, tamb&eacute;m em separado (uma ilustra&ccedil;&atilde;o&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>por arquivo). O mesmo procedimento dever&aacute; ser adotado para as tabelas, em&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>arquivo. doc.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>O artigo n&atilde;o poder&aacute; ultrapassar a 10.000 palavras ou 20 p&aacute;ginas, incluindo t&iacute;tulo,&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>autores, institui&ccedil;&otilde;es e e-mail, resumo e palavras-chave, abstract e keywords, texto,&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>figuras, tabelas, mapas, referencias e legendas. &nbsp; &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Nenhum arquivo poder&aacute; ultrapassar a 10Mb de tamanho. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Forma de envio: O &nbsp;texto dever&aacute; ser enviado junto com as &nbsp;ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es</big></span></span></span> <span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>(inclusive tabelas) nno Sistema Eletr&ocirc;nico de submiss&atilde;o (ver passos pr&aacute;ticos&nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>para envio de manuscritos na p&aacute;gina da RBGEA, no &iacute;tem "Instru&ccedil;&otilde;es para&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>envio de artigos").&nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>&nbsp; &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Artigos</big></span></span></span></strong></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o de artigos: dever&aacute; constar em seq&uuml;&ecirc;ncia, o t&iacute;tulo, nome&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>completo do(s) autor(es), institui&ccedil;&atilde;o e e-mail (nome da institui&ccedil;&atilde;o, cidade,&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>estado, pa&iacute;s e e-mail. Para &nbsp;alunos de mestrado ou doutorado, indicar&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>"Programa de P&oacute;s-gradua&ccedil;&atilde;o", institui&ccedil;&atilde;o, e demais informa&ccedil;&otilde;es acima),&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>resumo e palavras-chave, abstract e keywords, texto completo, refer&ecirc;ncias, ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es e tabelas. O texto deve conter, preferencialmente: introdu&ccedil;&atilde;o,&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>materiais e m&eacute;todos, resultados, discuss&atilde;o, conclus&otilde;es e agradecimentos.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Hierarquiza&ccedil;&atilde;o dos t&iacute;tulos e subt&iacute;tulos: Deve seguir o padr&atilde;o: </big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>&nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>N&iacute;vel 1 &ndash; EM NEGRITO, TODAS AS LETRAS MAI&Uacute;SCULAS. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>N&iacute;vel 2 &ndash; Em negrito; a primeira letra da primeira palavra em mai&uacute;scula e as&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>demais min&uacute;sculas. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>N&iacute;vel 3 - &nbsp;IT&Aacute;LICO, N&Atilde;O NEGRITO, TODAS AS LETRAS&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>MAI&Uacute;SCULAS. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>N&iacute;vel 4 &ndash; &nbsp;It&aacute;lico, n&atilde;o negrito; a primeira letra da primeira palavra em&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>mai&uacute;scula e as demais min&uacute;sculas. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Agradecimentos &ndash; &nbsp;Negrito e it&aacute;lico (apenas o subt&iacute;tulo). &nbsp;Refer&ecirc;ncias &ndash;&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Negritas e min&uacute;sculas (apenas o subt&iacute;tulo). &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Manter um espa&ccedil;o simples entre itens e subitens do texto. Utilizar fonte&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Times New Roman, tamanho 11.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>A indica&ccedil;&atilde;o da inser&ccedil;&atilde;o das ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es (figuras, tabelas, etc) no texto dever&aacute; ser em&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>posi&ccedil;&atilde;o o mais pr&oacute;ximo poss&iacute;vel de sua primeira cita&ccedil;&atilde;o. </big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Formato do Resumo, Resumen e o Abstract: N&atilde;o poder&atilde;o exceder 300&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>palavras cada, em par&aacute;grafo &uacute;nico, fonte Times New Roman, corpo 10,&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>espa&ccedil;o simples (1,0) e serem seguidos de palavras-chaves, palabras claves e&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>keywords (no m&iacute;nimo 3 e m&aacute;ximo 5), respectivamente. Artigos em&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>portugu&ecirc;s, espanhol ou franc&ecirc;s dever&atilde;o ter o t&iacute;tulo vertido para o idioma&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>ingl&ecirc;s, em MAI&Uacute;SCULO E IT&Aacute;LICO, colocado ap&oacute;s a palavra Abstract. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Formato do texto: Editar o texto em Word, fonte Times New Roman, corpo&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>11, espa&ccedil;o simples, papel A4, orienta&ccedil;&atilde;o em retrato e editado em apenas&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>uma coluna. As margens dever&atilde;o ter as seguintes medidas: superior: 2,0;&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>inferior 2,0; esquerda 3,0 e direita &nbsp;2,0. Digitar as tabelas em documentos&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>word. Abrevia&ccedil;&otilde;es: Devem ser evitadas ou mantidas ao m&iacute;nimo. Se usadas, devem&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>ser definidas na primeira vez que &nbsp;forem mencionadas e n&atilde;o devem ser&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>utilizadas no t&iacute;tulo, resumo e abstract.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es: A vers&atilde;o impressa da RBG &nbsp;publica ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es em preto e&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>branco e tons de cinza. A vers&atilde;o &ldquo;on line&rdquo; publica&ccedil;&otilde;es coloridas. As fontes&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>usadas para textos sobre fotografias deve ser uma da fam&iacute;lia da Helv&eacute;tica. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>As ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es gr&aacute;ficas, fotogr&aacute;ficas e fotomicrogr&aacute;ficas ser&atilde;o numeradas&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>seq&uuml;encialmente, na ordem de sua cita&ccedil;&atilde;o no texto e consideradas, mesmo pranchas,&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>indiscriminadamente como Figuras. Dever&atilde;o ser separadas do texto por uma linha.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>N&atilde;o ser&atilde;o aceitos encartes. Fotografias de afloramentos dever&atilde;o apresentar barra de&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>escala e indica&ccedil;&atilde;o do norte.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Letreiros e s&iacute;mbolos das ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es devem ter dimens&otilde;es adequadas para permitir&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>legibilidade. As ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es dever&atilde;o ter larguras &nbsp;m&iacute;nimas de 9 ou 18 cent&iacute;metros&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>(permitir diagrama&ccedil;&atilde;o em uma ou duas colunas). Explicar todos os s&iacute;mbolos.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Escalas gr&aacute;ficas, se necess&aacute;rias, devem ser colocadas dentro da &aacute;rea das ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>As &nbsp;Tabelas devem ser auto-explicativas, com as laterais abertas, concisas e&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>numeradas seq&uuml;encialmente. Devem ser elaboradas em Times New Roman, corpo 9.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>As legendas das ilustra&ccedil;&otilde;es dever&atilde;o ser redigidas com a mesma fonte do texto e&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>corpo.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Formato das Figuras: S&oacute; ser&atilde;o aceitas figuras &nbsp;.tif, devendo ter resolu&ccedil;&atilde;o m&iacute;nima&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>de 300dpi, com tamanhos largura de 8,7 cm ou de 17,7, com comprimento m&aacute;ximo&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>de 21 cm.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>F&oacute;rmulas e Equa&ccedil;&otilde;es: Numerar as f&oacute;rmulas e equa&ccedil;&otilde;es seq&uuml;encialmente &agrave;&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>direita, com n&uacute;meros ar&aacute;bicos entre par&ecirc;nteses e, no texto, referir como&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>&ldquo;equa&ccedil;&atilde;o (1)&rdquo;, etc. &nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>Cita&ccedil;&otilde;es no corpo do texto: &nbsp;Deve-se seguir os formatos do seguinte&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>exemplo: ..."Cunha (1985) interpreta a fei&ccedil;&atilde;o como uma estrutura de&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>resfriamento magm&aacute;tico</big></span></span></span> <span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>precoce, mas outros (Lima 1986, Fonseca &nbsp;et al.&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="font-size: smaller;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><big>1989, Ferreira &amp; Ara&uacute;jo 1994) como uma fei&ccedil;&atilde;o tardia". Refer&ecirc;ncias: Relat&oacute;rios internos s&atilde;o ser&atilde;o aceitos nas refer&ecirc;ncias, com&nbsp;</big></span></span></span><span style="color: #808080;"><span 